{"tid":1342411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"準備出元朗請入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:19:45.000Z","uid":264950,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab61146dd2f6e0d20537f1cb49850edfffc86f74","tid":1342411,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"我知單野令人憤怒，但今晚不宜作戰。原因如下<br />\n<br />\n1.人地有預謀，有裝備分分鐘係刀。如果冇裝就送頭，低級裝都送，如果高級裝就俾黑警搞<br />\n<br />\n2.人地養精蓄銳，我地作戰成日，會攰。<br />\n<br />\n3.我地臨時徵兵，連戰略都冇，組出來只係烏合之眾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係叫大家唔報仇，但打仗不是靠一時之勇。<br />\n所謂兵不厭詐，襯佢唔為意搞佢先最大效益。<br />\n<br />\n等有周詳計劃，分幾組人，分配工作<br />\n<br />\n如果今晚要入去，請救人為主。<br />\n報仇不要今晚。"},{"pid":"81be0ba4df8d52df92e8bf6a5f114097ba5eff8e","tid":1342411,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d751be50505fe45025a35c02ca6fcae0bfd132a","tid":1342411,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4af6a029f1a33d252ee72c2408106b6e95978f0f","tid":1342411,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:34:39.000Z","msg":"你幾時報仇佢都會出刀架啦"},{"pid":"52cefbbfcbfd674ff6b0e05329cffe74505d29a2","tid":1342411,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4af6a029f1a33d252ee72c2408106b6e95978f0f","tid":1342411,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:34:39.000Z","msg":"你幾時報仇佢都會出刀架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"你可以等佢半夜三間殺佢措手不及"},{"pid":"0c6950cc7addad0b3e7f64a6541df46ef37fcd42","tid":1342411,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"如果做好報仇覺悟，可以先起底，逐一擊破<br />\ne家黑鄉警大聯盟，企定定等你黎"},{"pid":"689a17e40acf5e7117d8f459070e636402d804eb","tid":1342411,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"求大家，日後還要大家的勇氣"},{"pid":"c51bc01eeac2d73890b4c485cdb1f204e